data.description: Do not miss this amazing opportunity! This home is situated in the Hidden Hills community, offering a great location w/ a dog park, walking trails, and no rear neighbors. It provides easy access to the 215 Beltway, nearby restaurants, shopping, and parks. Inside, you'll find an open and spacious floor plan, perfect for entertaining. The kitchen is a dream for entertainers, featuring stainless steel appliances, a quartzite island and countertops, and soft-close cabinets. Upstairs, you'll be impressed by the expansive loft and four roomy bedrooms, an oversized primary suite with his and hers walk-in closets, spacious primary bath with sep. tub and shower. With no rear neighbors, this yard provides a lot of privacy w/ a built-in patio cover and synthetic turf. Automatic blinds, a tankless water heater, washer, dryer, and fridge, makes this home move-in ready for you to enjoy and entertain! Newly constructed in 2022 very energy efficient saves you money!
